wr-ostree
=========

This layer provides ostree-support for WRLINUX.


Dependencies
------------
This layer depends on the openembedded-core and wrlinux layers.


Maintenance
-----------
This layer is maintained by Wind River Systems, Inc.
Contact <support@windriver.com> or your support representative for more
information on submitting changes.


Building with wr-ostree layer
---------------------------
This layer should be added to the bblayers.conf file.

Notes
-----
The layer is validate with Wind River intel-x86-64 BSP.

The following table summarizes the valid Wind River Linux distros for this layer.
'Y' in each content cell stands for supported; 'N' stands for not supported:

  +--------------+-------------+-------------+
  | valid/distro |   wrlinux   | wrlinux-cgl |
  +--------------+-------------+-------------+
  |    valid     |      Y      |      Y      |
  +--------------+-------------+-------------+

Due to ostree rootfs structure limitation, the layer can not working with
feature/intel-persistent-memory.